divs: Sighting Detailseverything started on the night of the 15th of October,2005 At around 10:30 PM,I was watching the sky (as is my usual habit)when suddenly,in a west to south direction,at a 60 degree angle,I saw a Fireball moving at slow speed,The fireball would stop for a few seconds at a time so that it took a few minutes (2 or 3) to cross the sky in from of me,At about 11:45 PM I decided to go to bed.Them at about 1:30 AM, I woke up to go to the bathroon and while in the bathroon I looked up through the skylight and realized that the Fireball was clearly visible on the left hand side of the Skylight.I observed the fire ball for about 5 minutes.It was standing still in the sky.by then it was the morning of the 16th of October 2005.I was still observing the fireball closely when I thought about looking for something with which to tape it,I found a camera and decid to take a photograph,I lowered the camera to observe the fireball on the photograph and saw that it was dark,the I decided to take a second photograph,and when I took it,I lowered the camera again to observe the photograph.Upon observing it,Ifound the great surprise and felt much fear.So much that I decided to shut off the camera and run to bed.The next day,in the clear of morning,I decided to ckeck out the camera to make sure that what I saw was the same as what I saw through screen.Yes what I saw was evidenced in the picture I took.It was the clear and distinct picture of what seemed like proyected E.T. faces.I dont know how they got there,close enough to peer through the Sky-light.I dont know if the proyection of the faces come from the fireball that was above me,over the the skylight.or what. the truth is,that I dont know what that was.
